Our room was spacious and very clean, and our bed was quite comfortable.	The room had a small window facing the street, and being at ground level, the view was not very good.	The hotel is lovely, the rooms beautifully decorated, spacious and very clean.	We had one of the gold rooms and it was very classy and clean.	The room we had was a superior on the first floor opposite the gorgeous red rooms.	The place was very clean and well appointed, lovely decor in our tiny standard room (the bathroom was huge and very nice).	Our room was charming and spacious; the bathroom was a bit small -- but convenient.